		</div>
	</div>
	<div class="social-comment-body">
				<p>Some of these issues do sound strange, and very annoying. I&#8217;ve never seen anything like that default browser problem you&#8217;ve described. Did you try trashing the related preference files?</p>
<p>In any case, just out of curiosity, what takes you to the Apple Menu so much?</p>
